data.meta_description: Picture agency for art. Photographs of paintings and other artworks from all periods of art history with a focus on European art.
data.text:
Search Help

Enter in the search box your search keyword or tag.

You can search by title, artist, location or technique. Example: Rembrandt

You can also combine search terms with each other. Example: St√§del Radierung Degas

Start your search with the Enter key or click on the Loupe .

With the cross you can empty the search field.

With the cogwheel you can filter your search result later.

Please note: with closing of all ARTOTHEK-windows and tabs your search history will be deleted.
